def insert_before_character(string):
    return string.replace('j', '1j')

print(insert_before_character('james'))  # Returns "1james"
print(insert_before_character('jelly'))  # Returns "1jelly"
print(insert_before_character('juice'))  # Returns "1juice"
print(insert_before_character('banana'))  # Returns "banana"
